  <h2 id="canvas">Canvas</h2>

  <p>
    These single-key shortcuts mirror the canvas board's bottom toolbar and an object's
    right-click menu. They fire only while a canvas board is focused, and never while you are
    typing in a query cell, text block, or the agent chat. Like every other shortcut, they are
    rebindable under <strong>Settings &rarr; Keyboard Shortcuts</strong> (the <strong>Canvas</strong>
    group), and the toolbar menus show whatever key you have bound.
  </p>

  <DocTable>
    <thead>
